"    dos2unix -o a.txt -n b.txt e.txt\n"
"\n"

#. type: textblock
#: dos2unix.pod:501
msgid "Convert c.txt and write to e.txt. Convert and replace a.txt.  Convert and replace b.txt. Convert d.txt and write to f.txt."
